Purchase Restrictions: Class R-6 shares are available in certain employer-sponsored retirement plans. See the prospectus for details.
        





Overview
		





Inflation protection and income.						  
By primarily investing in inflation-linked securities, the fund seeks to provide both inflation protection and income. It will have at least 80% of its assets invested in inflation-linked bonds.					





